OL,3,CITV follows Post Office drama with
OL,4,Cseries on infected blood scandal
OL,6,FSince the drama aired, former Post
OL,7,FOffice chief executive Paula Vennells
OL,8,Fpromised to hand back her CBE
OL,9,Ffollowing an explosion in signatories
OL,10,Fon an online petition and the
OL,11,Fgovernment promised to speed-up
OL,12,Fcompensation.
OL,14,FWhat is the Infected Blood scandal?
OL,16,FIn the 1970s and 80s, blood product
OL,17,F'Factor 8' was sourced from high risk
OL,18,Fdonors in America like prisoners, drug
OL,19,Faddicts and sex workers to treat
OL,20,Fpatients in the UK.
