OL,6,FTo date, more than 3,000 people who
OL,7,Fcontracted illnesses have died.
OL,9,FA public inquiry was set up in 2017 -
OL,10,Fhearing evidence from hundreds of
OL,11,Fpeople affected - before its final
OL,12,Frecommendations to compensate them
OL,13,Fwere made last year.
OL,15,FThe final report for the Infected
OL,16,FBlood Inquiry comes out in May. The
OL,17,Finquiry has already made its final
OL,18,Frecommendations for compensation for
OL,19,Fvictims and their loved ones.
