OL,6,FWhen Prime Minister Rishi Sunak
OL,7,Fappeared before the inquiry last year,
OL,8,Fhe vowed to pay compensation "as
OL,9,Fswiftly as possible".
OL,11,FWhat is the drama about?
OL,13,FITV announced on Thursday that Peter
OL,14,FMoffat will write the new drama about
OL,15,Fthe infected blood scandal.
OL,17,FMoffat won two Baftas for BBC series
OL,18,FCriminal Justice and has also created
OL,19,Fthe screenplay for upcoming Netflix
OL,20,Ffilm, Scoop, about the Duke of York's
OL,21,FNewsnight interview.
