OL,3,CITV follows Post Office drama with
OL,4,Cseries on infected blood scandal
OL,6,FITV's head of drama, Polly Hill, said:
OL,7,F"Peter's scripts are brilliant and do
OL,8,Fjustice to this important story, while
OL,9,Fbringing it to screen with real
OL,10,Fclarity and compassion."
OL,12,FCollins Solicitors represents 1,500
OL,13,Fvictims and their families. Des
OL,14,FCollins, senior partner of the firm,
OL,15,Fsaid he believes the series "will
OL,16,Frefocus public attention on the
OL,17,Ftragedy of the infected blood scandal."
