OL,6,F"It will expose much of what our
OL,7,Fclients have endured, not only
OL,8,Femotionally and health-wise, but also
OL,9,Fin terms of shoddy treatment by
OL,10,Fgovernment, in their decades-long
OL,11,Fbattle for justice during which too
OL,12,Fmany lives have unnecessarily been
OL,13,Flost," he added.
OL,15,F"Viewers won't fail to be moved by
OL,16,Fthis compelling story of the worst
OL,17,Ftreatment scandal in NHS history.
OL,18,FSadly, it remains a devastating
OL,19,Freality for many.
